title: Iwin Games - Mark & Mandi's Love Story - New Puzzle [h33t][Wend
description:
Mark & Mandi&#039;s Love Story


Mark & Mandi&#039;s Love Story is an innovative spot the difference game with hidden-object twists. Help Cupid find out the differences between Mark and Mandi, and build four gorgeous wish gardens to advance their charming love story.
n Mark & Mandi&#039;s Love Story, you get to help Cupid find the differences between a couple of crazy kids in love. Build four gorgeous wish gardens where they can fall in love, and experience four creative and fun mini games that vividly describe those special moments in their journey to happiness. Enjoy six different image puzzle gameplays, from the innovative find the difference and spot the similarity games, to classic jigsaw puzzles. Like Romeo and Juliet & Antony and Cleopatra, Mark & Mandi&#039;s Love Story will go down in history...hopefully, with your help, it will end a little better!
